      <title>首尔情报机构称金正恩之女正在接受继任培训</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/north-korea-kim-s-daughter-likely-his-successor-south-korea-s-spy-agency-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国情报机构向国会议员表示，朝鲜领导人金正恩的十几岁女儿正在接受执政培训，这对于不到两年前首次进入公众视野的女孩来说，是一个快速提升的过程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/north-korea-kim-s-daughter-likely-his-successor-south-korea-s-spy-agency-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:12:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
